content.rendered:
Ormeau Florist

Make all your floral dreams come true with LULLY & ROSE, your specialty florist in Ormeau. Discover our exclusive range of seasonal, custom-designed floral arrangements that showcase the finest florals, and our unique range of artisanal add-on gifts. 

Luxury Florist

Here at LULLY & ROSE Floral Studio we work with the seasons, so you can be sure that no two floral bouquets or posies will ever be the same. Trust our experienced lead floral designer and owner, Rachael, to select the very best of what’s available and create something stunning just for you or your loved one. As a local florist offering delivery to Ormeau, it’s important to us to support other locals! That’s why we handpick our florals from the local flower markets, and source locally grown wherever possible. You can also choose to purchase one of our “Send & Support Locally Grown” varieties, to ensure your supporting a local grower are in Queensland and Australia.

When you shop online with LULLY & ROSE, you’ll receive same-day delivery on orders placed before 11am AEST. Orders sent out from our Ormeau florist are packaged with water and hand delivered with care. Experience the LULLY & ROSE difference today by placing an order from our extensive online range:

Whether you’re sending flowers to a loved one, or simply treating yourself to a touch of floral beauty, LULLY & ROSE Floral Studio is your trusted florist for same day deliveries to Ormeau.

Our Floral Selections
  • Designer Posies
  • Designer Bouquets
  • Designer Vase Arrangements
  • Floral Bowl
  • Gift Hampers
  • En Masse
  • Fragrant & Sweet
  • Locally Grown Tulips
  • Local Grown Dahlias
  • Send Love & Hugs
  • Cut Phalaenopsis Stem
  • Cut Cymbidium Stem
  • Phalaenopsis Orchid Plants

Get In Touch

After something in particular, or planning an event? Get in touch with our Ormeau florist by emailing info@lullyandrose.com.au to discuss all things florals. We’d love to be a part of your special moments. We have been honoured to provide our luxury flower arrangements and thoughtfully curated gift hampers and add-on gifts for a variety of occasions: newborn baby arrivals, get well flowers, hospital deliveries, weddings, engagements, house warmings, Mother’s Day flowers, Valentine’s Day flowers, and all the ‘just because’ days in between. Send flowers online with LULLY & ROSE Floral Studio.

As a leading Ormeau florist, LULLY & ROSE has developed a signature style that lets flowers speak where words are just not enough. Our approach to design is inspired by the latest trends in European and Australian floristry. Combined with a sincere love for the meaning behind flowers and a (not so) small obsession with the colour white. All of our flower arrangements are packaged in a minimalistic style, with crisp white paper and a chic rose gold ribbon or can be delivered in a contemporary glass vase for an extra special gift. Each flower bouquet is designed with love as well as care.

To help you go the extra mile when treating yourself or your loved ones, we’ve also curated the best artisan gifts from around Australia. These are available as an add-on gift to your order, or as part of one of our themed gift hampers.

Enjoy our flower delivery service to neighbouring areas like Pimpama and Upper Coomera, and share the beauty of florals beyond Ormeau. With same day flower delivery for all orders placed before 11am, AEST.

SHOP HERE
